data.title: New Mexico Department of Health
data.meta_description: The mission of New Mexico Department of Health is to promote health and wellness, improve health outcomes, and assure safety net services for all people in New Mexico.

Sierra County public health office provides back-to-school vaccinations

The Sierra County Public Health Office at 201 East Fourth Avenue in Truth or Consequences will be providing no cost back-to-school vaccinations for all children aged 18 and younger throughout July with no appointment necessary.

Las Cruces public health office provides back-to-school vaccinations
